12
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,120
You're not trying to avoid responsibility, are you?

13
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:35,240
What exactly happened?

14
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:43,000
The symptoms will disappear in ten minutes.

15
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,520
I'll be going now, Mr. Lin.

16
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,720
Are you angry because

17
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:18,680
I didn't do anything

18
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,400
last night?

19
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,720
Then why are you still here?

20
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,920
Is this how you treat your

21
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,520
life-saving hero?

22
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,240
Why weren't you this fierce when you

23
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,000
