24
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:42,120
I thought there might be something wrong with the wine,

25
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:44,280
I even had the waiter replace the wine.

26
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:45,960
But I didn't expect

27
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:47,800
Duan Chenglin to put the drug in the cup.

28
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,800
Anyway,

29
00:05:50,280 --> 00:05:51,440
don't put yourself

30
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,440
in danger again.

31
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,760
Because it hurts me.

32
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:27,640
[Affair between brother-in-law and sister-in-law]

33
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,640
[This morning,]

34
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:30,320
[Lin Group was exposed to an ethics storm.]

35
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,520
[Lanhe Group's CEO, Lan Hewei,]

36
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,920
